s Claude cheaper than ChatGPT?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"At the consumer tier, both Claude Pro and ChatGPT Plus cost $20 per month. At the API level, Claude 3.5 Sonnet and GPT-4o are similarly priced. Claude 3 Haiku is one of the most affordable high-quality models available from any major provider, making Claude competitive for high-volume API use cases."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What does a team of 10 budget for Claude per year?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A team of 10 on Claude Team at $30/seat/month pays $300/month or $3,600/year for the subscription. If the team also uses the API for custom workflows, add variable API costs on top. Most small teams building internal tools spend $400 to $800/month all-in during the first year."}}]}</script>
